dc_description_s: This data layer represents parcels for Portage County, Wisconsin in 2014. [The Parcel data set is a vector representation of tax parcel boundaries and associated parcel attributes in Portage County, Wisconsin. The parcels are created by using coordinate geometry and digitizing from digital orthophotography.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most recent version of this data, please visit: https://www.co.portage.wi.gov/375/Land-Information-GIS
